 immunosuppressive or myelosuppressive agents should be avoided if possible.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/25044/', '', 'Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Cladribine, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', 'Anakinra, Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', 1767369485);
